-- Fidelity Contrafund cuts Yahoo stake by 41 pct this year  
-- By Tim McLaughlin
-- Mon Jun 02, 2014 10:58AM EDT
-- None



BOSTON, June 2 (Reuters) - Fidelity Investments Contrafund <FCNTX.O>, the largest mutual fund investor in Yahoo Inc <YHOO.O>, cut its stake in the Internet media company by 41 percent during the first four months of 2014, according to the fund's latest disclosure on holdings.

